</font><font size="5" face="Arial">S</font><font face="Arial">ilverado
Gold Mines Ltd. is a publicly traded company in the business of
exploring, developing and mining precious metal deposits. The
Company is headquartered in Vancouver, B.C., Canada, and has
property interests in Alaska and British Columbia. Silverado
shares are traded on NASDAQ (Ticker Symbol: <b>GOLDF</b>). </font></p>

